title: Norgekart N50 - Topographical map of Norway
description:
NORGEKART N50 - MAP OF NORWAY
====================================
Type:              Topographical map
Format:            JPEG
Coordinate system: UTM Zone 32
Resolution:        5 m/pixel
Year:              2008
====================================

This is N50, a detailed topographical map of mainland Norway (excluding
Svalbard and Jan Mayen). It has all streets and trails marked.

To provide one single map all of Norway has been projected into the
coordinate system for UTM Zone 32, although some parts should be in
other zones. This may cause some slight distortion in the easternmost
parts of the map.

If you are planning a hike in the mountains, remember that although
mountains and lakes often stay at the same place huts and trail markers 
can be moved or removed - always bring a recent map!

The map is in the JPEG/JGW format and should work with most map software.
If it doesn't work with yours there are free tools to convert to lots of
other formats.

Please help seeding!
